{"tid":704511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社評論指美國挑起貿易戰失信於人輸了世界","createTime":"2018-06-16T14:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T01:43:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"581d5d778ba21df782054700674c701e35671853","tid":704511,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"中美爆發貿易戰，互相向對方500億美元進口貨加徵關稅。新華社發表評論文章，批評美國挑起貿易戰，是失信於人輸了世界，理應遭到全世界聯合抵制。文章指，美國並非只針對中國，面對利益下，曾經的盟友和合作夥伴隨時可變成競爭者，無論是退出巴黎氣候協定，或執意退出伊朗核協議，或對歐盟、加拿大、墨西哥等鋼鋁產品徵稅，或拒絕承認G7峰會聯合公報，美國的邏輯只有是符合美國優先戰略，可跟任何人翻臉，但美方應記住國與國之間交往，不同跟企業做生意，不是一次性買賣，用對付企業的辦法對付國家，最後必將落得四面楚歌，陷於孤立。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，妥協、退讓、求和最終只會讓好戰者有恃無恐，得寸進尺。中國必須與各國一道共同抵制，避免讓整個世界再為美國單邊主義錯誤行徑買單，防止讓世界貿易秩序，退到叢林法則。"},{"pid":"e63b041ac4f65c5090e9e921b7dba8fda9b89757","tid":704511,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bde605c8ac68cfed096b2095ba3ec4926f5133","tid":704511,"uid":188252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"贏國算唔算干涉他國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55c21ff2f1136bcd1556f271444e05ce67a9e79","tid":704511,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"Marco Rubio<br />\n@marcorubio<br />\n&middot;<br />\n2h<br />\n#China started trade war blocking U.S. companies,stealing their intellectual property &amp; forcing hand over of technology. Now they respond to ⁦new #TheftTax with tariffs that will raise price of food on their people. Lets see how that works out for them <br />\n<br />\nChina Issues Retaliatory Tariffs as Trade Fight Heats Up<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/white-house-announces-tariffs-on-50-billion-of-goods-from-china-1529065534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.w